    "description": "Steel Racer is a 2D pixelated old school racing game, inspired by classics from the 80s and 90s era, featuring great chiptune music, arcade gameplay style and high speed cars!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRace through 50 different circuits along 5 racing seasons! On each season, you can choose the order of the races you want to compete! Win races and money to improve and customize your car and become a racing legend!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou'll be able to choose between 3 difficulty settings and 3 levels of traction assist, which makes your car easier or harder to control on curves, and make the game as challenging as you would like!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAre you ready to become the &quot;Steel Racer&quot;!?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFEATURES<br />\r\n- 50 different tracks;<br />\r\n- 5 racing seasons featuring different scenarios;<br />\r\n- 2D retro style graphics; <br />\r\n- Different items to buy and improve/customize your car;<br />\r\n- Great chiptune style music;",
